  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Below are the selection of restaurants and bars available at the Pestana Miramar, please note that not all of these restaurants are included in the half-board and full-board offering, some will be payable and bookable locally.</p>
<p>On the half-board or full-board offering, dinner can be enjoyed in the A Vila buffet restaurant or in the Adega restaurant. The Miramar restaurant is not included in half-board or full-board but you can receive €15 credit per person to use at the restaurant, the remaining cost of the meal is payable locally and you must book in advance. Those on full-board can enjoy lunch at the Bar da Proa.</p>
<p><strong>Miramar restaurant</strong> is open selected days of the week offering an a la carte menu. It's designed to replicate the rooms in a traditional house. </p>
<p><strong>Restaurant “A Villa”</strong> is open for breakfast and dinner and offers a buffet that includes a range of national and international cuisine. This restaurant is included in the half-board package.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Pausa Burger</strong> is open at lunch time and serves some tasty treats including burgers.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Adega</strong> offers lots of charm and character to go with it’s traditional Maderian dishes.</p>
<p><strong>Bar Miramar</strong> is traditional in style and the perfect place to grab a drink before dinner.</p>
<p><strong>Bar A Proa</strong> is great for grabbing a lunch time drink as well as a light lunch or snacks.</p>
<p><strong>Cocktail bar A Fonte</strong> is open in the evening’s and has a really fun atmosphere with live music and dancing everyday.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
