  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studio Superior Miramar Rooms</strong> sleep up to two people and are approx. 32m². They offer either a double bed or twin beds (please specify preference when booking). Enjoy swimming pool or garden views from the balcony or terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Family Miramar Rooms</strong> sleep up to three people and are approx. 42m². They offer either a double bed or twin beds (please specify preference when booking), the extra bed is a sofa bed. There is a small living room with sofa bed and kitchenette.</p>
<p><strong>Suite Miramar Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are approx. 76m². They offer either a double bed or twin beds (please specify preference when booking). Rooms are situated in the manor house and offer traditional architectural features.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>Kitchenette</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>From the 1st of June 2024 a tourist tax of approx. €2.00 per person per night, for a maximum of 7 nights is payable locally for guests age 13 years and over (subject to change).</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
